NovaPay is an international financial service that provides Ukrainians with financial services online and through the Nova post branch network, connecting families and friends and boosting Ukrainian business in the world. Our offices are located in Ukraine, Moldova and Lithuania.

We offer financial products in both online and offline formats to individuals and businesses, including:
▪ taking care of payments at Nova post and financing for packages;
▪ delivering money transfers within Ukraine and abroad;
▪ accepting utility and any other payments;
▪ providing internet acquiring and partnership services for businesses.

The NovaPay payment system is the leader among all non-banking institutions in Ukraine in terms of remittances (according to the National Bank of Ukraine).

NovaPay LLC was registered in Ukraine in 2012, and we are currently actively expanding in EU countries.

👥 Our team consists of over 1,000 professionals across Ukraine and beyond.
